---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Solana Breakpoint 2022 — AES" bodyClass="inner-page">

  <div class="container-fluid event-hero">
    <div class="event-hero-inner">
      <div class="event-hero-left">
        <div class="event-location">Lisbon, Portugal</div>
        <div class="event-title">Solana<br />Breakpoint<br />2022</div>
        <div class="event-tagline">
          Building on the success of the 2021 program, we expanded the footprint across Lisbon to include 5 venues for over 4,000 delegates.
        </div>
        <div class="event-hero-photo">
          <div class="event-hero-photo-item" style="background-image: url('/images/work1.png')"></div>
          <div class="event-hero-photo-item" style="background-image: url('/images/work2.png')"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="event-hero-right">
        <div class="event-detail-card">
          <div class="event-detail-block">
            <div class="event-detail-heading">Production</div>
            <p>Due to the popularity of events in Lisbon by the fall of 2022, venues were more difficult to source. Our main venue, Carlos Lopes Pavilion, was one of the main venues for Web Summit, which immediately precedes Breakpoint. Our production team managed to fully set and test our main stage in less than 18 hours.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="event-detail-block">
            <div class="event-detail-heading">Registration</div>
            <p>Pre-registration took place outside of Carlos Lopes Pavilion while the team was setting up inside. We brought in 10 branded containers the morning of registration and were fully ready to open in less than 4 hours time.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="event-detail-block">
            <div class="event-detail-heading">On-Site</div>
            <p>A larger footprint means a larger team. This year we employed 1 venue manager and 1 registration manager per venue along with upwards of 30 temporary staff per venue. We also expanded the transportation schedule and had two developer-focused stages.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container-fluid event-gallery">
    <div class="event-gallery-inner">
      <div class="gallery-grid">
        <div class="gallery-placeholder gallery-large" style="background-image: url('/images/work3.png')"></div>
        <div class="gallery-placeholder" style="background-image: url('/images/work5.png')"></div>
        <div class="gallery-placeholder" style="background-image: url('/images/work7.png')"></div>
        <div class="gallery-placeholder gallery-large" style="background-image: url('/images/work9.png')"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container-fluid event-back">
    <div class="event-back-inner">
      <a href="/work" class="cr-btn white ex-padding">← Back to All Events</a>
    </div>
  </div>

</BaseLayout>
